flowchart TB
  Web[Next.js React Web] -->|REST SSE| API[NestJS Fastify API]
  API --> Temporal[Temporal]
  Temporal --> Connectors[TypeScript Connector Workers]
  Temporal --> AI[Python AI and Simulation Workers]
  API --> PG[(PostgreSQL plus pgvector)]
  API --> Graph[(Neo4j)]
  API --> Cache[(Valkey)]
  Connectors --> PG
  Connectors --> Objects[(S3 compatible objects)]
  AI --> PG
  AI --> Graph
  AI --> Llama[Meta Llama API primary]
  AI -. evaluated optional route .-> OpenAI[OpenAI Responses API]
  PG -->|Transactional outbox| Relay[Event Relay]
  Relay --> Graph
  Relay --> Search[Search Projection]
  Web -. telemetry .-> OTel[OpenTelemetry]
  API -. telemetry .-> OTel
  Connectors -. telemetry .-> OTel
  AI -. telemetry .-> OTel
